# Home-Automation
Using Bluetooth module(HC-05) and AMR voice app, different loads are turned ON/OFF on voice command.
The code is written in C language using arduino IDE.
This project aims to control home appliances by voice commands.
The main advantage of implementing home automation using voice commands is that user convinience.
It can also be used by disabled people and also blinds so that they can easily get used to home automation.
